    "created_at": "2016-03-05T08:26:13Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-03-05T08:26:13Z",
    "body": "I can reproduce the same bug in Chrome browser, I think there is probably an optimisation that delays the rendering of hidden window, but I can not find related code or issues.\n\nI suggesting reporting this to Chromium's issues list or seeking help from the chromium-dev mailing list instead, because the rendering is completely on Chromium's side and there is nothing we can do in Electron.\n"
